"help.text"
msgid "The status bar displays information about your document, including the currently selected object. You can double-click some status bar items to open a related dialog window."
msgstr "ແຖບສະຖານະສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ, ລວມທັງວັດຖຸທີ່ຖືກເລືອກໃນປັດຈຸບັນ. ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ບາງລາຍການໃນແຖບສະຖານະເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. D5pvR
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Rulers"
msgstr "ໄມ້ບັນທັດ"

#. 3A6CF
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"bm_id3153191\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>rulers; in presentations</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>origin of rulers</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ໄມ້ບັນທັດ; ໃນການນຳສະເໜີ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດ</bookmark_value>"

#. L9A6B
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153191\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/simpress/main0209.xhp\">Rulers</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/simpress/main0209.xhp\">ໄມ້ບັນທັດ</link>"

#. CidBg
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3149666\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can use vertical and horizontal rulers at the left and upper edges of the $[officename] Impress workspace to assist you in creating your slide. The sections of the rulers that cover the area of the slide are white."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໄມ້ບັນທັດແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ແນວນອນ ຢູ່ຂອບເບື້ອງຊ້າຍ ແລະ ເບື້ອງເທິງ ຂອງພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ $[officename] Impress ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃນການສ້າງສະໄລ້ຂອງທ່ານ. ພາກສ່ວນຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດທີ່ກວມເອົາພື້ນທີ່ຂອງສະໄລ້ຈະເປັນສີຂາວ."

#. r9DKG
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3153963\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you select an object, its dimensions are displayed on the rulers as gray double lines. To precisely resize the object, drag one of the double lines to a new location on the ruler."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງ, ຂະໜາດຂອງມັນຈະຖືກສະແດງໃນໄມ້ບັນທັດເປັນເສັ້ນຄູ່ສີເທົາ. ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂະໜາດວັດຖຸໃຫ້ຊັດເຈນ, ໃຫ້ລາກເສັ້ນຄູ່ເສັ້ນໃດໜຶ່ງໄປຫາຕຳແໜ່ງໃໝ່ໃນໄມ້ບັນທັດ."

#. tPZfC
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3150206\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you select a text object on a slide, indents and tabs are displayed on the horizontal ruler. To change the indent or tab settings for the text object, drag an indent or a tab marker to a new location on the ruler."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກວັດຖຸຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນສະໄລ້, ການຍັບຍໍ້ໜ້າ ແລະ ແຖບຕັ້ງຈະຖືກສະແດງໃນໄມ້ບັນທັດແນວນອນ. ເພື່ອປ່ຽນການຕັ້ງຄ່າຍັບຍໍ້ໜ້າ ຫຼື ແຖບຕັ້ງສຳລັບວັດຖຸຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ໃຫ້ລາກເຄື່ອງໝາຍການຍັບຍໍ້ໜ້າ ຫຼື ແຖບຕັ້ງ ໄປຫາຕຳແໜ່ງໃໝ່ໃນໄມ້ບັນທັດ."

#. mcRAk
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3150253\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also drag a <link href=\"text/simpress/01/04030000.xhp\">snap line</link> from a ruler to help you align objects on your slide. To insert a snap line using a ruler, drag the edge of a ruler into the slide."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດລາກ <link href=\"text/simpress/01/04030000.xhp\">ເສັ້ນຈັບຍຶດ</link> ຈາກໄມ້ບັນທັດເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃນການຈັດວາງວັດຖຸໃນສະໄລ້ຂອງທ່ານ. ເພື່ອແຊກເສັ້ນຈັບຍຶດໂດຍການໃຊ້ໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດເຂົ້າໄປໃນສະໄລ້."

#. TY2DC
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3153820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To show or hide the rulers, choose <link href=\"text/simpress/01/03060000.xhp\"><emph>View - Rulers</emph></link>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອສະແດງ ຫຼື ເຊື່ອງໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/simpress/01/03060000.xhp\"><emph>ມຸມມອງ - ໄມ້ບັນທັດ</emph></link>."

#. kYDwa
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3148609\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To specify the measurement units for a ruler, right-click the ruler, and then choose a new unit from the list."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລະບຸຫົວໜ່ວຍວັດແທກສຳລັບໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ແລ້ວເລືອກຫົວໜ່ວຍໃໝ່ຈາກລາຍການ."

#. 9SAnD
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3149129\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the origin (0 point) of the rulers, drag the intersection of the two rulers in the top left corner into the workspace. Vertical and horizontal guides appear. Continue to drag until the vertical and horizontal guides are where you want the new origin to be, and then release. To reset the origins of the rulers to the default values, double-click the intersection."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ (ຈຸດ 0) ຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ໃຫ້ລາກຈຸດຕັດກັນຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດທັງສອງຢູ່ມຸມເທິງເບື້ອງຊ້າຍເຂົ້າໄປໃນພື້ນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກ. ເສັ້ນແນະນຳແນວຕັ້ງ ແລະ ແນວນອນຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນ. ໃຫ້ລາກຕໍ່ໄປຈົນກວ່າເສັ້ນແນະນຳທັງສອງຈະຢູ່ໃນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ເປັນຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃໝ່, ແລ້ວປ່ອຍ. ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດຄືນເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ຈຸດຕັດກັນ."

#. uPJ4a
#: main0209.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0209.xhp\n"
"par_id3154651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the slide margins, drag the edge of the white areas in the rulers."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂອບສະໄລ້, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບຂອງພື້ນທີ່ສີຂາວໃນໄມ້ບັນທັດ."

#. GtNCm
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drawing Bar"
msgstr "ແຖບການແຕ້ມ"

#. sdzeS
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150342\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/simpress/main0210.xhp\">Drawing Bar</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/simpress/main0210.xhp\">ແຖບການແຕ້ມ</link>"

#. sfxro
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3150202\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">The <emph>Drawing</emph> bar contains frequently used editing tools. Click the arrow next to an icon to open a toolbar that contains additional commands.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ແຖບ <emph>ການແຕ້ມ</emph> ປະກອບມີເຄື່ອງມືການແກ້ໄຂທີ່ໃຊ້ເລື້ອຍໆ. ຄລິກທີ່ລູກສອນຂ້າງໄອຄອນເພື່ອເປີດແຖບເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ມີຄຳສັ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມ.</ahelp>"

#. k2kCs
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id31502029\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can view the Drawing bar also from a text document or spreadsheet. The set of visible icons can be slightly different according to the current document type."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເບິ່ງແຖບການແຕ້ມໄດ້ຈາກເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ສະເປຣດຊີດ. ຊຸດໄອຄອນທີ່ປາກົດອາດຈະແຕກຕ່າງກັນເລັກນ້ອຍຕາມປະເພດເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. C3EJZ
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155962\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select"
msgstr "ເລືອກ"

#. 4FwUb
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3148488\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select an object on the current slide, click the <emph>Select</emph> tool (white arrow) on the Drawing bar, and then click the object."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸໃນສະໄລ້ປັດຈຸບັນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການເລືອກ</emph> (ລູກສອນສີຂາວ) ໃນແຖບການແຕ້ມ, ແລ້ວຄລິກທີ່ວັດຖຸ."

#. GVEUE
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3148610\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select more than one object, hold down Shift while you click."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງວັດຖຸ, ໃຫ້ກົດ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຄລິກ."

#. NbWE3
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3148699\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select an object that is behind another object, hold <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>, and then click the object. To select the next underlying object in the stacking, hold <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>, and then click again. To return the selection to the previously selected object, hold down Shift + <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>, and then click."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸທີ່ຢູ່ທາງຫຼັງວັດຖຸອື່ນ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້, ແລ້ວຄລິກທີ່ວັດຖຸ. ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸຖັດໄປທີ່ຢູ່ຊັ້ນລຸ່ມ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ແລ້ວຄລິກອີກບາດໜຶ່ງ. ເພື່ອເລືອກຄືນວັດຖຸກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ໃຫ້ກົດ Shift + <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ ແລ້ວຄລິກ."

#. 4aToU
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3154651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To add text to a selected object, double-click the object and type or enter your text."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມໃສ່ວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ວັດຖຸ ແລ້ວພິມຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງທ່ານ."

#. nKzEE
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_id3153812\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To remove a selection, click anywhere outside the selected object, or press Escape."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກການເລືອກ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ຢູ່ນອກວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກ, ຫຼື ກົດ Escape."

#. kvp4W
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_idN106B0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/simpress/02/10060000.xhp\">Rectangle</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/simpress/02/10060000.xhp\">ຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ</link>"

#. BgdH4
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_idN106C0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Draws a filled rectangle where you drag in the current document. Click where you want to place a corner of the rectangle, and drag to the size you want. To draw a square, hold down Shift while you drag."
msgstr "ແຕ້ມຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກທີ່ມີການເຕີມສີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານລາກໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ. ຄລິກບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການວາງມຸມຂອງຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ, ແລ້ະລາກໄປຫາຂະໜາດທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເພື່ອແຕ້ມຮູບຈະຕຸລັດ, ໃຫ້ກົດ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລາກ."

#. 8q8av
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_idN106CD\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/simpress/02/10070000.xhp\">Ellipse</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/simpress/02/10070000.xhp\">ຮູບວົງມົນຮີ</link>"

#. AFZzm
#: main0210.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0210.xhp\n"
"par_idN106DD\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Draws a filled oval where you drag in the current document. Click where you want to draw the oval, and drag to the size you want. To draw a circle, hold down Shift while you drag."
msgstr "ແຕ້ມຮູບວົງຮີທີ່ມີການເຕີມສີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານລາກໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ. ຄລິກບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຕ້ມຮູບວົງຮີ, ແລ້ະລາກໄປຫາຂະໜາດທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເພື່ອແຕ້ມຮູບວົງມົນ, ໃຫ້ກົດ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລາກ."

