#. 3ciws
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146119\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"main0503\"><link href=\"text/simpress/main0503.xhp\">$[officename] Impress Features</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"main0503\"><link href=\"text/simpress/main0503.xhp\">ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງ $[officename] Impress</link></variable>"

#. ifaB7
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3151074\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Impress lets you create professional slide shows that can include charts, drawing objects, text, multimedia and a variety of other items. If you want, you can even import and modify Microsoft PowerPoint presentations."
msgstr "$[officename] Impress ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສ້າງການສະແດງສະໄລ້ແບບມືອາຊີບທີ່ສາມາດລວມເອົາແຜນພູມ, ວັດຖຸການແຕ້ມ, ຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ມັລຕິມີເດຍ ແລະ ລາຍການອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດນຳເຂົ້າ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂການນຳສະເໜີຂອງ Microsoft PowerPoint ໄດ້ອີກດ້ວຍ."

#. bAxiz
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3149379\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For on-screen slide shows, animation, slide transitions and multimedia are a few of the techniques you can use to make your presentation more exciting."
msgstr "ສຳລັບການສະແດງສະໄລ້ໃນໜ້າຈໍ, ພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ, ການປ່ຽນສະໄລ້ ແລະ ມັລຕິມີເດຍ ແມ່ນເຕັກນິກບາງຢ່າງທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການນຳສະເໜີຂອງທ່ານໜ້າຕື່ນເຕັ້ນຂຶ້ນ."

#. jKSma
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154016\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating Vector Graphics"
msgstr "ການສ້າງກຣາຟິກແບບເວັກເຕີ"

#. SHdFk
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3154485\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Many of the tools for creating vector graphics in $[officename] Draw are available in $[officename] Impress."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຫຼາຍຢ່າງສຳລັບການສ້າງກຣາຟິກແບບເວັກເຕີໃນ $[officename] Draw ແມ່ນມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນ $[officename] Impress."

#. fEEfD
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150208\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating Slides"
msgstr "ການສ້າງສະໄລ້"

#. RCCha
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3153247\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Impress provides you with templates to create professional-looking slides."
msgstr "$[officename] Impress ມີແມ່ແບບໃຫ້ທ່ານເພື່ອສ້າງສະໄລ້ທີ່ເບິ່ງເປັນມືອາຊີບ."

#. UGbcC
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3148610\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also assign a number of dynamic effects to your slides, including animation and transition effects."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດກຳນົດເອັບເຟັກແບບໄດນາມິກໃຫ້ກັບສະໄລ້ຂອງທ່ານ, ລວມທັງພາບເຄື່ອນໄຫວ ແລະ ເອັບເຟັກການປ່ຽນສະໄລ້."

#. D4ctS
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating Presentations"
msgstr "ການສ້າງການນຳສະເໜີ"

#. cS3Au
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3153917\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Several views or pages are available when you design a slide show. For example, the Slide Sorter displays an overview of your slides in thumbnail form, while the Handout page contains both the slide and the text you want to distribute to the audience."
msgstr "ມີຫຼາຍມຸມມອງ ຫຼື ໜ້າທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານອອກແບບການສະແດງສະໄລ້. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ການຈັດລຽງສະໄລ້ຈະສະແດງພາບລວມຂອງສະໄລ້ໃນຮູບແບບຮູບຫຍໍ້, ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໜ້າເອກະສານແຈກຢາຍຈະປະກອບມີທັງສະໄລ້ ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຈກຢາຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ຊົມ."

#. CRoEP
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3148608\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Impress also lets you rehearse the timing of your slide show."
msgstr "$[officename] Impress ຍັງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຊ້ອມເວລາຂອງການສະແດງສະໄລ້ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້."

#. qqweR
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154649\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Publishing Presentations"
msgstr "ການເຜີຍແຜ່ການນຳສະເໜີ"

#. EcVzV
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3150046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can publish your slides on-screen, as handouts, or as HTML documents."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເຜີຍແຜ່ສະໄລ້ຂອງທ່ານໃນໜ້າຈໍ, ເປັນເອກະສານແຈກຢາຍ, ຫຼື ເປັນເອກະສານ HTML ໄດ້."

#. uk4z5
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146965\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Giving Presentations"
msgstr "ການສະເໜີຜົນງານ"

#. TzAuK
#: main0503.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0503.xhp\n"
"par_id3145114\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Impress gives you the choice of running a slide show automatically or manually."
msgstr "$[officename] Impress ໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກໄດ້ວ່າຈະເລີ່ມການສະແດງສະໄລ້ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ ຫຼື ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. F98f9
#: main_slide.xhp
