msgctxt ""
"main_slide.xhp\n"
"par_id841615491449943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the slide has a background image, this option allows the user to save the corresponding background image file."
msgstr "ຖ້າສະໄລ້ມີຮູບພາບພື້ນຫຼັງ, ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ຮູບພາບພື້ນຫຼັງນັ້ນໄດ້."

#. Bhh37
#: main_slide.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main_slide.xhp\n"
"hd_id161615489786339\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set Background Image"
msgstr "ກຳນົດຮູບພາບພື້ນຫຼັງ"

#. ekbFN
