msgstr "ປ່ຽນຊື່ສະໄລ້"

#. GpHBE
#: main_slide.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main_slide.xhp\n"
"par_id901615495187958\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens a dialog box where a name can be set for the current slide."
msgstr "ເປີດກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສາມາດຕັ້ງຊື່ສຳລັບສະໄລ້ປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. D6GtH
#: main_slide.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main_slide.xhp\n"
"hd_id551615489789347\n"
"help.text"
