msgstr "<link href=\"text/simpress/submenu_object_shape.xhp\">ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ຮູບຊົງ</link>"

#. aBtgV
#: submenu_object_shape.xhp
msgctxt ""
"submenu_object_shape.xhp\n"
"par_id111615131426235\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens a submenu to edit the properties of the selected textbox or shape."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູຍ່ອຍເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຮູບຊົງທີ່ເລືອກ."
